    public class MultiTournamentModel
extends DefaultListenable<MultilateralTournamentConfiguration>
    Contains the basic elements of MultilateralTournamentConfiguration, but mutable and the subcomponents are listenable so that we can use it for the MVC pattern. It listens to changes in the protocol and updates the model when necessary.

    You can get notified when the multitournamentmodel is complete (as indicated by the user, he can press 'start' in the GUI). The data passed with the notification is the MultilateralTournamentConfiguration.
